          <img src="{{ root_path }}img/works_placereactionstudies_btn.jpg" alt="An example of a Place Reaction Study installation in the foyer at UWE" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="nav-caption">An examination of how a place or situation can be affected by abstract geometric shapes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="small-12 large-6 columns">
      <div class="nav">
        <a href="{{ root_path }}works/imagereactionstudies.html">
          <span>Image Reaction Studies</span>
          <img src="{{ root_path }}img/works_imagereactionstudies_btn.jpg" alt="An example of an image which was altered using the abstract spins." />
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="nav-caption">A further exploration of meaning of abstract shapes using pre-made images.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
